latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Glam up time with MARS!💕 Our Martian @psychedinthecity
has created this amazing #romanticglam look for you guys. 😍
.
.
.

Here's how to create this look:

♥️1) Prime your face with our Mars Glow O' Clock #primer for a flawless face and healthy skin.
♥️2) Blend your base perfectly using our Mars wonder #beautyblender.
♥️3) Apply soft petals and green shades from #mermaid palette. Blend these shades well.
♥️4) Apply Mars Ice your eyes #liquideyeshadow in the shade Moon Glow on your eyelids and inner corners to give your eyeshadow an oomph.
♥️5) Highlight your highpoints of your face with Mars Rainbow Shinning Baked #blush .
